FBIS4-37747 "drnes122_a_94003" FBIS-NES-94-122 Daily Report 18 Jun 1994 ARAB AFRICA Algeria Violent Incidents Continue Throughout Country Violent Incidents Continue Throughout Country Family Murdered in Ain Defla Province LD1806135394 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 1200 GMT 18 Jun 94 LD1806135394 Algiers Radio Algiers Network Arabic BFN [Text] The horrible murder of members of a family were carried out by armed men in Zerdin municipality in Ain Defla province. The family, which consisted of a 70-year-old father, his wife, and their 30-year-old son were shot and killed.
